      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. It looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the factory, with flawless paint, a pristine interior, and a perfectly functioning mechanical system. Every feature works flawlessly, and there are absolutely no signs of wear, scratches, or mechanical issues. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in impeccable, like-new condition.",
