    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It has been a dependable car, but it is priced to reflect these necessary maintenance items and cosmetic blemishes.",
