      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80 chassis features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, utilizing its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration for a broad torque curve. Power is managed via the Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the rear wheels through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The vehicle maintains its structural rigidity and original double-wishbone suspension geometry, ensuring the precise handling characteristics the platform is known for. Recent service includes a timing belt replacement and a full cooling system refresh. While the finish shows minor road wear, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent compression and linear boost pressure, making this a prime candidate for a driver-focused enthusiast.",
