    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained 2019 all-wheel-drive SUV that perfectly bridges the gap between utility and luxury. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic silver that still catches the light beautifully, with only minor, superficial stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of curb rash. Step inside to a pristine, smoke-free interior featuring charcoal leather seating that remains supple and free of cracks or bolster wear. All interior electronics, including the premium sound system, heated seats, and backup camera, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. We have strictly followed the manufacturer's maintenance schedule, with the most recent service including a fresh oil change and a comprehensive fluid top-off. The tires offer approximately 70% tread life, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This vehicle represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality ride without the new-car price tag. Full service history documentation is available upon request.",
